					"body": "{html}<div><p>(from <a href=\n\"/projects/32238/changesets/b4b1b8e8c742baccd4b6f80472efdc6e9e36cc15\"\ntitle=\n\"Changeset [b4b1b8e8c742baccd4b6f80472efdc6e9e36cc15]\">[b4b1b8e8c742baccd4b6f80472efdc6e9e36cc15]</a>)\n[<a href=\"/projects/32238/tickets/1524\" title=\n\"Ticket #1524\">#1524</a> state:fixed-in-qa]: Don't relayout while\nwe're animating. <a href=\n\"https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/b4b1b8e8c742baccd4b6f80472efdc6e9e36cc15\">\nhttps://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/b4b1b8e8c742...</a></p></div>{html}",
