					"body": "{html}<div><p>(from <a href=\n\"/projects/32238/changesets/69900554e38b4bb674cf07cefe8a2d4eaf37c193\"\ntitle=\n\"Changeset [69900554e38b4bb674cf07cefe8a2d4eaf37c193]\">[69900554e38b4bb674cf07cefe8a2d4eaf37c193]</a>)\n[<a href=\"/projects/32238/tickets/2348\" title=\n\"Ticket #2348\">#2348</a> state:fixed-in-qa][<a href=\n\"/projects/32238/tickets/1524\" title=\"Ticket #1524\">#1524</a>\nstate:open] Unfixing <a href=\"/projects/32238/tickets/1524\" title=\n\"Ticket #1524\">#1524</a>. Cure was worse than disease. May have led\nto other regressions. <a href=\n\"https://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/69900554e38b4bb674cf07cefe8a2d4eaf37c193\">\nhttps://github.com/appcelerator/titanium_mobile/commit/69900554e38b...</a></p></div>{html}",
